                                <seg type="supplication">ለጸሐፎ፡ ኃጥእ፡ <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12874Anorewos">አኖሬዎስ፡</persName> ወለዘአጽሐፎ፡ <persName role="patron" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12873MazmuraD"><roleName type="title">አባ፡</roleName> መዝሙረ፡ ድንግል፡</persName> 
